2x^2+5x-1 \enclose{longdiv}{6x^3+9x^2-17x+11}\\

-x^2-15x+11\\
\underline{-\left(-x^2-5x+1\right)}\\
-10x+12
\end{align*}

The sum of the quotient and remainder is $3x-2-10x+12 = -7x+10$.
